\frac{a^2}{b}+\frac{b^2}{c}+\frac{c^2}{a}+\frac{3n}{a^2+b^2+c^2} \geq 3+n
a^2+b^2+c^2 \geq a+b+c \geq 3 
 \frac{a^2}{b}+\frac{b^2}{c}+\frac{c^2}{a} \geq {(a + b +c)(a^2 + b^2 + c^2)\over ab + bc +ac} = {(a + b +c)(a^2 + b^2 + c^2)\over (a+b+c)} = a^2 + b^2 +c^2
{a^2 + b^2 + c^2 = z}
f(z, n) = z + {3n \over z}
n \leq 3
z \geq 3
n < 3
f'(z) = 0 \implies z = \sqrt{3n } < 3 \leq z
f'(z \geq 3) > 0
f(z)
z=3
f(z,n) = z + {3n \over z} \geq  6 \text{ for n=3}
